  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA72">
<l>mutalān tiruvuruva mūṉṟeṉpa roṉṟē</l>
<l>mutalāku mūṉṟukku meṉpar mutalvā</l>
<l>nikarilaku kāruruvā niṉṉakatta taṉṟē</l>
<l>pukarilaku tāmaraiyiṉ pū.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The holy forms that were the beginning are three, they say. Only one</l>
<l>of the three was the beginning, they say. O First one,</l>
<l>you of equally shining cloud form, is it not inside you,</l>
<l>the flower of the tawny shining lotus?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
